{"tid":1463253,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"機場文宣請入","createTime":"2019-08-13T12:32:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T12:54:30.000Z","uid":54014,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1d35bed8b4501f84d37646d384121122254c63d4","tid":1463253,"uid":54014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:32:08.000Z","msg":"大家既然去得機場，唔係單單話塞住旅客，重要等外國人知道香港咩事，要點幫。<br />\n但我地有我地講五大訴求，佢地返到去又可以點幫我地呢？<br />\n至少要呼籲佢地咁做：<br />\n1.幫手簽聯署(petition)，有關五大訴求盡簽，<a href=\"http://change.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fchange.org&d=2QIn9Yr%2BOYfG2lc2ZV7v%2BtqeVONt7zbw7GHn8%2FjWPdo%3D&h=089ba3d2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">change.org</a>又好白宮聯署都好。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.change.org/petitions?selected=popular_weekly\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.change.org%2Fpetitions%3Fselected%3Dpopular_weekly&d=2QIn9Yr%2BOYfG2lc2ZV7v%2BtqeVONt7zbw7GHn8%2FjWPdo%3D&h=c6cbd8db\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.change.org/petitions?selected=popular_weekly</a><br />\n2.促請政府制裁香港(sanction)，及表明要香港撤回「送中條例」、實行雙普選。<br />\n英文：Completely withdraw Extradition Bill. Immediately implement Dual Universal Suffrage.<br />\n特別係英、美國，要叫政府執行「中英聯合聲明」同「香港人權與民主法案」！<br />\n英文：Sino-British Joint Declaration同Hong Kong Human Rights and Democracy Act<br />\n3.抵制所有公司賣武器(weapon/crowd control equipment)畀香港警察，包括法國、德國同美國。<br />\n德國：衝鋒槍MP5（示威無用過）<br />\n法國：水炮車(water cannon vehicles)<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180522/bkn-20180522151306317-0522_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180522%2Fbkn-20180522151306317-0522_00822_001.html&d=2QIn9Yr%2BOYfG2lc2ZV7v%2BtqeVONt7zbw7GHn8%2FjWPdo%3D&h=f87935ad\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180522/bkn-20180522151306317-0522_00822_001.html</a><br />\n美國：催淚彈(Tear gas)MP-6M5-CS，橡膠子彈(Rubber bullet)MP-4-R3 Hard Rubber Batons，催淚彈槍37/38mm Federal Riot Gun，散彈槍Remington Model 870。<br />\n<a href=\